{
  "total_duration": 733.804,
  "lines": [
    {
      "i": 0,
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 12.176,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "今天的题目是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Across the Channel"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，中文是“横渡海峡”。先别把"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Channel"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "想成电视台、视频频道或者 app 频道。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 1,
      "start": 12.526,
      "end": 29.117,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这里的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "the English Channel"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是英吉利海峡，也就是 France 和 England 中间的一片海。Debbie 要做的事情，是从"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "the French coast"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "出发，横渡这片海，到"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "the English coast"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 2,
      "start": 29.467,
      "end": 41.683,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "你可以先在脑子里画一张很简单的地图：左边是 France，右边是 England，中间是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "the English Channel"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，箭头是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "France to England"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 3,
      "start": 42.033,
      "end": 50.353,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "Debbie Hart 只有 eleven years old。明天早上 five o'clock，她准备开始这次 long-distance open-water swim。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 4,
      "start": 50.702,
      "end": 63.622,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "但是这课不是“一个孩子突然热血冒险”。它更像一份认真计划：years of training，father in a small boat，short rests every two hours，friends waiting on the English coast。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 5,
      "start": 63.972,
      "end": 80.212,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "现实里，公开水域长距离游泳需要 professional training，adult support，support boat，weather judgment，还有完整安全计划。我们欣赏 Debbie 的目标感，但不能把它当成普通孩子可以自己模仿的挑战。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 6,
      "start": 80.562,
      "end": 100.442,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "整课记忆链是：Channel -> French coast -> five a.m. -> eleven -> world record -> strong swimmer -> father boat -> trained for years -> anxious watch -> rests, drink, no solid food -> friends wait -> mother swam it too。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 7,
      "start": 100.792,
      "end": 107.968,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第一幅画，是路线和出发时间。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Debbie Hart is going to swim across the English Channel tomorrow."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 8,
      "start": 108.318,
      "end": 121.358,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "across"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是 from one side to the other，从一边到另一边。这里就是从 France 这一边，游过"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "the English Channel"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，到 England 那一边。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 9,
      "start": 121.708,
      "end": 127.579,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "课文接着说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "She is going to set out from the French coast at five o'clock in the morning."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 10,
      "start": 127.929,
      "end": 139.233,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "set out"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是 start a journey，出发。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "the French coast"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是法国海岸，不是法国城市中心，而是靠海的边缘。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 11,
      "start": 139.583,
      "end": 152.703,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "所以第一幅画要像一张儿童能看懂的小地图：French coast 在一边，English coast 在另一边，中间是一条蓝色海峡路线，Debbie 准备在清晨五点出发。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 12,
      "start": 153.053,
      "end": 161.141,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第二幅画，是目标和训练。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Debbie is only eleven years old and she hopes to set up a new world record."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 13,
      "start": 161.491,
      "end": 170.242,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这里的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "record"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是 world record，世界纪录，不是 recording audio，也不是 video record。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 14,
      "start": 170.592,
      "end": 176.284,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "课文说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "She is a strong swimmer and many people feel that she is sure to succeed."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 15,
      "start": 176.634,
      "end": 184.554,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "sure to succeed"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "的意思是 very likely to succeed，大家觉得她很可能成功。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 16,
      "start": 184.904,
      "end": 193.448,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "但这份信心不是从天上掉下来的。后面有一个关键原因："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Mr. Hart has trained his daughter for years."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 17,
      "start": 193.798,
      "end": 205.382,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这里的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "train"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是训练、指导、练习，不是火车。Debbie 是 child with a big goal，但背后有 years of training。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 18,
      "start": 205.731,
      "end": 211.915,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第三幅画，是支持计划。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Debbie's father will set out with her in a small boat."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 19,
      "start": 212.265,
      "end": 222.665,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "父亲不是在岸上随便看热闹。他会坐 small support boat 跟着 Debbie，因为 open water 有 distance，cold water，waves，weather 和 boats。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 20,
      "start": 223.015,
      "end": 229.427,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "课文说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Tomorrow he will be watching her anxiously as she swims the long distance to England."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 21,
      "start": 229.777,
      "end": 237.721,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "anxiously"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "不是不相信她，而是 care plus worry：他支持她，也担心她的安全。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 22,
      "start": 238.071,
      "end": 243.871,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "Debbie 自己也有计划："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Debbie intends to take short rests every two hours."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 23,
      "start": 244.22,
      "end": 253.452,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "She will have something to drink but she will not eat any solid food."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这说明她不是乱游，她知道怎么分配体力、休息和补水。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 24,
      "start": 253.802,
      "end": 262.29,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第四幅画，是终点和家庭故事。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Most of Debbie's school friends will be waiting for her on the English coast."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 25,
      "start": 262.64,
      "end": 271.736,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "will be waiting"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "让我们想象：Debbie 还在海里游的时候，同学们已经在英国海岸一直等着她。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 26,
      "start": 272.086,
      "end": 279.094,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "最后一句很暖："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Among them will be Debbie's mother, who swam the Channel herself when she was a girl."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 27,
      "start": 279.444,
      "end": 290.132,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Among them will be Debbie's mother"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是一种比较正式的倒装句，意思是 her mother will be among them，她妈妈也在那群等待的人里面。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 28,
      "start": 290.481,
      "end": 304.081,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "结尾不是笑点，而是 family tradition：Debbie 的妈妈小时候也横渡过海峡。这个挑战很大，但它不是突然冒险，而是训练、支持和家庭传承连在一起。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 29,
      "start": 304.431,
      "end": 309.951,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "我们先确认一个地理问题："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "the English Channel"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "到底是什么？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 30,
      "start": 310.301,
      "end": 313.214,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是一个电视台或者视频频道吗？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 31,
      "start": 313.564,
      "end": 321.467,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "不是。这里的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Channel"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是海峡，英吉利海峡，在 England 和 France 中间。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 32,
      "start": 321.817,
      "end": 330.357,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "所以"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "the French coast"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "到"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "the English coast"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，就是从法国海岸到英国海岸？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 33,
      "start": 330.707,
      "end": 336.187,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "对。这个"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "across"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "就是从一边到另一边。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 34,
      "start": 336.537,
      "end": 340.043,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "Debbie 只有 eleven years old，这会不会太危险？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 35,
      "start": 340.393,
      "end": 351.273,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "所以课文特别写了 support plan。她是 strong swimmer，父亲 has trained her for years，而且 father will set out with her in a small boat。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 36,
      "start": 351.623,
      "end": 355.953,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "anxiously"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是不是说明爸爸很害怕？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 37,
      "start": 356.303,
      "end": 364.783,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "更准确地说，是又支持又担心。父母有时候就是这样：they believe in you, but they still watch carefully。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 38,
      "start": 365.133,
      "end": 368.794,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "最后妈妈也在岸边，这个细节为什么重要？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 39,
      "start": 369.144,
      "end": 381.344,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "因为她小时候也 swam the Channel herself。结尾让这件事从 world record 变成 family story：big goal, years of training, support team, and people waiting for you。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 40,
      "start": 381.694,
      "end": 385.894,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Debbie Hart is going to swim across the English Channel tomorrow."
        }
      ]
    },
